      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mb-6">
        <a href="mailto:karuna.mangla@gmail.com?subject=Corporate%20Training%20Inquiry" class="btn-primary text-sm">
          Email Karuna
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/karuna-mangla" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary text-sm">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
